      "x": 250, "y": 30, "width": 520, "height": 148,
      "text": "PHASE 0: Requirements Approval\n(pre-condition — partially complete)\n\n✓ Task Sheet scripts + passing tests\n✓ YAML → Sheets import pipeline\n⏳ Trial: QR → mobile form (TC-5, TC-6)\n⏳ Trial: sign-up sheet with stewards\n⏳ Capture method selection (§5.3)",
