    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "track1_text",
      "x": 30, "y": 233, "width": 425, "height": 245,
      "text": "Track 1 — Architecture Document\n\n* System context + 4-pipeline boundaries\n* 9 system + 4 human actors (§2.2–2.3)\n* Slack channel structure: 5 channels (§7.2)\n* Permission model: roles matrix (§7.3)\n* Sheets: tasks + completions +\n  members tables (M1/O1 gap, §9)\n* Deployment topology (Python, APScheduler)\n* Security: Slack channel access control\n\n[Open: Claude patterns, Sheets schema,\nmobile form design, notification routing]",
      "originalText": "Track 1 — Architecture Document\n\n* System context + 4-pipeline boundaries\n* 9 system + 4 human actors (§2.2–2.3)\n* Slack channel structure: 5 channels (§7.2)\n* Permission model: roles matrix (§7.3)\n* Sheets: tasks + completions +\n  members tables (M1/O1 gap, §9)\n* Deployment topology (Python, APScheduler)\n* Security: Slack channel access control\n\n[Open: Claude patterns, Sheets schema,\nmobile form design, notification routing]",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#047857", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 2007, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 2007001,
