    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "track2_text",
      "x": 565, "y": 233, "width": 425, "height": 245,
      "text": "Track 2 — Prototype Sprints (throwaway)\n\n* P1 Claude API: NL query parsing, OCR\n  vision, latency, context management\n* P2 Slack Bolt: #shop-admin commands,\n  channel routing, event subscriptions\n* P3 Google Sheets: write latency, rate\n  limits, service account auth (TC-2)\n* P4 Mobile Form: QR→POST, ≤2-tap\n  flow (TC-5, TC-6), no-login UX",
      "originalText": "Track 2 — Prototype Sprints (throwaway)\n\n* P1 Claude API: NL query parsing, OCR\n  vision, latency, context management\n* P2 Slack Bolt: #shop-admin commands,\n  channel routing, event subscriptions\n* P3 Google Sheets: write latency, rate\n  limits, service account auth (TC-2)\n* P4 Mobile Form: QR→POST, ≤2-tap\n  flow (TC-5, TC-6), no-login UX",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
