    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase2_text",
      "x": 210, "y": 540, "width": 600, "height": 178,
      "text": "PHASE 2: Architecture Convergence (1 week)\n\nKey decisions:\n* Capture method: confirm Method 3, retire OCR?\n* Claude integration: stateless vs. stateful?\n* Sheets writes: real-time vs. batch + retry?\n* Add members sheet now? (M1/O1 KPIs, §9)\n* Mobile form hosting: bot process or separate?\n* Notification fan-out pattern finalized\n\n→ Architecture doc finalized + sign-off",
      "originalText": "PHASE 2: Architecture Convergence (1 week)\n\nKey decisions:\n* Capture method: confirm Method 3, retire OCR?\n* Claude integration: stateless vs. stateful?\n* Sheets writes: real-time vs. batch + retry?\n* Add members sheet now? (M1/O1 KPIs, §9)\n* Mobile form hosting: bot process or separate?\n* Notification fan-out pattern finalized\n\n→ Architecture doc finalized + sign-off",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
