    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase3_text",
      "x": 230, "y": 778, "width": 560, "height": 162,
      "text": "PHASE 3: Task Database Pipeline\n\nSpec: tasks/completions/members schema,\nSlack command formats, validation rules (DB-5, DB-6)\n\n* Sheets service account auth setup\n* YAML bulk-load → tasks sheet (DB-2)\n* #shop-admin add/update/delete commands (DB-3)\n* Permission enforcement: steward = own location (DB-4)\n* #shop-alerts notification on every change (DB-7)",
      "originalText": "PHASE 3: Task Database Pipeline\n\nSpec: tasks/completions/members schema,\nSlack command formats, validation rules (DB-5, DB-6)\n\n* Sheets service account auth setup\n* YAML bulk-load → tasks sheet (DB-2)\n* #shop-admin add/update/delete commands (DB-3)\n* Permission enforcement: steward = own location (DB-4)\n* #shop-alerts notification on every change (DB-7)",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
