    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase4_text",
      "x": 230, "y": 996, "width": 560, "height": 148,
      "text": "PHASE 4: Task Sheet Pipeline\n\nSpec: sheet command format, PDF handoff to existing scripts\n\n* sheet <location> | all — generate PDF (TS-1, TS-3)\n* #shop-bulletin: post when sheet ready (TS-4)\n* #shop-alerts: log every generation (TS-5)\n* APScheduler: refresh reminder on task change (TS-6)\n\n[Depends on Phase 3]",
      "originalText": "PHASE 4: Task Sheet Pipeline\n\nSpec: sheet command format, PDF handoff to existing scripts\n\n* sheet <location> | all — generate PDF (TS-1, TS-3)\n* #shop-bulletin: post when sheet ready (TS-4)\n* #shop-alerts: log every generation (TS-5)\n* APScheduler: refresh reminder on task change (TS-6)\n\n[Depends on Phase 3]",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#047857", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
