    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase5_text",
      "x": 230, "y": 1199, "width": 560, "height": 178,
      "text": "PHASE 5: Task Capture Pipeline\n\nSpec: mobile form POST contract, QR URL format,\ncompletions write spec (TC-1–TC-6)\n\n* Mobile form: no login (TC-6), ≤2 taps (TC-5)\n* POST → completions sheet (TC-2: immediate)\n* #shop-log confirmation (TC-3), #shop-alerts (TC-4)\n* QR code per location (Method 3)\n* OCR fallback: Claude vision, UNKNOWN placeholders\n\n[Depends on Phases 3–4]",
      "originalText": "PHASE 5: Task Capture Pipeline\n\nSpec: mobile form POST contract, QR URL format,\ncompletions write spec (TC-1–TC-6)\n\n* Mobile form: no login (TC-6), ≤2 taps (TC-5)\n* POST → completions sheet (TC-2: immediate)\n* #shop-log confirmation (TC-3), #shop-alerts (TC-4)\n* QR code per location (Method 3)\n* OCR fallback: Claude vision, UNKNOWN placeholders\n\n[Depends on Phases 3–4]",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 2, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
