    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "phase6_text",
      "x": 230, "y": 1432, "width": 560, "height": 198,
      "text": "PHASE 6: Task Reporting Pipeline\n\nSpec: Claude NL prompt, 4 report types,\nAPScheduler schedule, KPI contracts (M1–M3, O1–O4)\n\n* #shop-queries NL handler via Claude (TR-1)\n* Reports: Member, Location, Shop, Compliance\n* #shop-alerts on each report generation (TR-4)\n* Monthly: compliance summary (TR-5),\n  top-contributors (TR-6)\n* Weekly: errors/availability report (TR-7)\n* Suspend/restore actions (area/shop scope)\n\n[Depends on all previous phases]",
      "originalText": "PHASE 6: Task Reporting Pipeline\n\nSpec: Claude NL prompt, 4 report types,\nAPScheduler schedule, KPI contracts (M1–M3, O1–O4)\n\n* #shop-queries NL handler via Claude (TR-1)\n* Reports: Member, Location, Shop, Compliance\n* #shop-alerts on each report generation (TR-4)\n* Monthly: compliance summary (TR-5),\n  top-contributors (TR-6)\n* Weekly: errors/availability report (TR-7)\n* Suspend/restore actions (area/shop scope)\n\n[Depends on all previous phases]",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#6d28d9", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
